    <item>
      <title>[AI工具从入门到入土] docker</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/post/ai%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E4%BB%8E%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8%E5%88%B0%E5%85%A5%E5%9C%9F/docker/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/post/ai%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E4%BB%8E%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8%E5%88%B0%E5%85%A5%E5%9C%9F/docker/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[AI工具从入门到入土] docker</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h1 id="基本命令">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%9f%ba%e6%9c%ac%e5%91%bd%e4%bb%a4"></a>
基本命令
</h1><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-gdscript3" data-lang="gdscript3"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 设置开机启动docker</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">systemctl</span> <span class="n">enable</span> <span class="n">docker</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 重启docker</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">systemctl</span> <span class="n">restart</span> <span class="n">docker</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 镜像:</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">images</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">search</span> <span class="n">xxx</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">pull</span> <span class="n">xxx</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">rmi</span> <span class="n">xxx</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 容器:</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">run</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">it</span> <span class="o">--</span><span class="n">name</span> <span class="n">XXX</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">v</span> <span class="o">...</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="o">...</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">xxx</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mf">5.0</span> <span class="o">/</span><span class="n">bin</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">bash</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">run</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">id</span> <span class="o">--</span><span class="n">name</span> <span class="n">XXX</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">v</span> <span class="o">...</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="o">...</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">xxx</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mf">5.0</span> <span class="o">/</span><span class="n">bin</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">bash</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">exec</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">it</span> <span class="n">XXX</span> <span class="o">/</span><span class="n">bin</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">bash</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">exit</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">start</span> <span class="n">XXX</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">ps</span> <span class="c1"># 当前容器</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">ps</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">a</span> <span class="c1"># 所有容器</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">stop</span> <span class="n">XXX</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">rm</span> <span class="n">XXX</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 加载镜像</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">commit</span> <span class="err">容器</span><span class="n">id</span> <span class="err">镜像名称</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="err">版本号</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">save</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">o</span> <span class="err">压缩文件名</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">tar</span> <span class="err">镜像名称</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="err">版本号</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="nb">load</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">i</span> <span class="err">压缩文件</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 根据Dockerfile来构建镜像</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">docker</span> <span class="n">build</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">f</span> <span class="o">./</span><span class="n">Dockerfile</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">t</span> <span class="n">xxx</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mf">1.0</span> <span class="o">.</span> <span class="c1"># .代表寻址的路</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><h1 id="创建容器">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%88%9b%e5%bb%ba%e5%ae%b9%e5%99%a8"></a>
创建容器
</h1><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">docker run -id --gpus all --name SY311 -v /home/qsun/桌面/SY:/root/SY sy311:4.0 /bin/bash
</span></span></code></pre></div>$$
\text{
docker run -id --gpus all --name SY311 -v \color{red}/home/qsun/桌面/SY\color{black}:\color{green}/root/SY \color{purple}sy311:4.0 \color{black}/bin/bash
}
\\
\begin{cases}
\color{red}外部主设备的项目文件夹路径(需要提前准备好)
\\
\color{green}容器内部的对应文件夹目录(会自动创建)
\\
\color{purple}镜像名与其对应版本
\end{cases}
$$<blockquote>
<p>当创建容器后, 红色文件夹(实际存在) 与 绿色文件夹(容器内存在) 会关联起来
-&gt; 修改主机内实际存在的文件夹, 则容器内的该文件夹也会变</p>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-05-17首发于<a href='http://localhost:1313/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-05-17</p>]]>
